      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2005-04-06</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2005-04-21T19:34:27Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Investment Tax Simplification Act of 2005 - Makes permanent the reduction in individual capital gains tax rates enacted by the Jobs and Growth Tax Relief Reconciliation Act of 2003.</p> <p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to reduce the maximum capital gains tax rates for individuals and corporations.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
